OL,3,CEnergy bills rise further than
OL,4,Cexpected, as Ofgem increases price cap
OL,5,Cby 2%
OL,7,FEnergy regulator Ofgem confirmed on
OL,8,FWednesday it was increasing the price
OL,9,Fcap on energy providers by 2%, paving
OL,10,Fthe way for higher household energy
OL,11,Fbills this Autumn.
OL,13,FThe increase was more than analysts
OL,14,Fhad previously predicted, as just last
OL,15,Fweek experts at Cornwall Insight
OL,16,Fpredicted the typical household energy
OL,17,Fbill will rise by #17 to #1,737 per
OL,18,Fyear.
