OL,14,Fincreases it expected a small drop in
OL,15,Fthe price cap in January, but this was
OL,16,Fdependent on geopolitical movement,
OL,17,Fweather patterns, changes to policy
OL,18,Fcosts and the potential introduction
OL,19,Fof costs such as those to support
OL,20,Finvestment in new nuclear generating
OL,21,Fcapacity.
