OL,7,FLast week, Dr Craig Lowrey, principal
OL,8,Fconsultant at Cornwall Insight, said:
OL,9,F"News of higher bills will not be
OL,10,Fwelcomed by households, especially as
OL,11,Fwinter approaches.
OL,13,F"While the added costs behind this
OL,14,Fforecasted rise are aimed at
OL,15,Fsupporting those most in need, it does
OL,16,Fmean typical bills will increase
OL,17,Fdespite relatively lower wholesale
OL,18,Fcosts. It is a reminder that the price
OL,19,Fcap reflects more than just the market
OL,20,Fprice of energy.
