OL,3,CEnergy bills rise further than
OL,4,Cexpected, as Ofgem increases price cap
OL,5,Cby 2%
OL,7,FOfgem, which sets the limit on what
OL,8,Fenergy companies can charge customers,
OL,9,Fchanges the price cap for households
OL,10,Fevery three months, largely based on
OL,11,Fthe cost of energy on wholesale
OL,12,Fmarkets.
OL,14,FThe government introduced the price
OL,15,Fcap in January 2019, setting a maximum
OL,16,Fprice that energy suppliers can charge
OL,17,Fconsumers in England, Scotland and
OL,18,FWales for each kilowatt hour of energy
OL,19,Fthey use.
